\begin_layout Subsection

\lang english
Fixed Mix Rule
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
A possible policy rule is to implement a strategy with a fixed amount of
 total capital in each of the three possible assets (cash, stock, and bonds)
 with a fixed amount in the overlay commodities index.
 This rule can be good for long term investing, but does not take into account
 Jennifer's age or how close she is to attaining her goals.
 
\end_layout

